data.description: Welcome to your beautiful move-in-ready home! The Ryan Homes - Griffin Hall style Villa boasts three levels of fine living: new patterned carpet throughout, new hardwood floors on the main level, beautifully painted cabinets in the kitchen and bathrooms, and brand new window blinds, topped off with a fresh coat of paint. The top level offers a spacious loft area to relax and entertain, two large bedrooms with spacious walk-in closets, a bonus room for a bedroom or study, and a full bathroom. The home's main level offers open-concept living with a kitchen with plenty of cabinetry and counter space for large items, a spacious dining and living room, and a very roomy owner's suite with a huge ensuite and walk-in closet. The enormous basement includes a full bathroom, an oversized storage room, and a walk-out leading to the big backyard with a beautiful stone patio. The community offers superb resort-like living with a fitness center, walking/biking trails, a tennis court, etc. Another great benefit of living in Brunswick Crossing is that Villa homeowners do not cut grass! So, what are you waiting for? Come on home!
